        Dimension getDimension​()
        Returns:
        Returns the dimension given at construction.

      • addTag

        void addTag​(DataTag newTag)
        Adds the tag to this IDataInfo object. You should only call this method if you created this IDataInfo (You should not call this for IDataInfo you receive. Make a new instance with the DataInfoFactory and then add your tag to that).

      • addTags

        void addTags​(DataTag[] newTags)
        Convenience method to add all of the given tags. You should only call this method if you created this IDataInfo (You should not call this for IDataInfo you receive. Make a new instance with the DataInfoFactory and then add your tag to that).

      • clearTags

        void clearTags​()
        Removes all tags. You should only call this method if you created this IDataInfo.

      • getTags

        DataTag[] getTags​()
        Returns the array of tags held by this DataInfo instance. The same instance of the array can be returned each time the method is called, so the array elements should not be modified.

      • getFactory

        IDataInfoFactory getFactory​()
        Returns a mutable factory that can make copies of this instance of DataInfo.
